\id 3JN - Sari
\h 3 Jи”и”е‹
\toc1 Kiе‹waati ki kiе‹ga kitи›и›tи› ki Jи”и”е‹ lи›
\toc2 3 Jи”и”е‹
\toc3 3Jе‹
\mt2 Kiе‹waati ki kiе‹ga kitи›и›tи› ki
\mt1 Jи”и”е‹ lи›
\imt1 Fiee fi nuuе‹ lи› Kiе‹waati ki kiе‹ga kitи›и›tи› ki Jи”и”е‹ lи› kini-i
\ip Jи”и”е‹ wu teenyi yi yee le te kikoo wu kintaashи›-и› ki bи›niiе‹ bи› kimbeenchи›-и›, tи›лқ tsи›и› kiе‹waati kee ki kiе‹ga kitи›и›tи› kini li wi wumu wu limfwe li kintaashи›-и› ki bи›niiе‹ bи› kimbeenchи›-и› bukooе‹ bwee nuuе‹ le Gayи”е‹. Tи›лқ tsи›и› piи›ti Gayи”е‹ li mfiи› wu tи›лқ fii bи›niiе‹ bи› mbeenchи›-и›. Tи›лқ tiifi tи› Gayи”е‹ le ni dzeti mfi kii wi wumu wu bи› tи›лқ teenyi le Diotefи›s wu tи›лқ fи›е‹gi е‹'wowu jи› ye.
\iot Bikoo bi biee bi lи› Kiе‹waati kini-i
\io1 1-4 Mbи›и›chи›
\io1 5-8 Jи”и”е‹ pia Gayи”е‹
\io1 9-10 Jи”и”е‹ guе‹ kiе‹ge ki Diotefи›-и›s
\io1 11-12 Jи”и”е‹ pia kiе‹ge ki Dи›mи›trus
\io1 13-15 Kimи›risи›
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 фҚ mi wu te kikoo wu kintaashи›-и› ki bи›niiе‹ bи› kimbeenchи›-и›. Ntsи›kи”и” kiе‹waati kini li wи› Gayи”е‹ wu sinи›е‹ wu sheлғе‹. еҳkи”е‹gisи”и” wи› li chи›и›е‹ li.
\s1 Jи”и”е‹ pia Gayи”е‹
\p 
\v 2 Sinи›е‹ wu sheлғе‹, nlи›kи”и” li Nyи”-и” le biee bichu ni bi giiе‹gi bujи”е‹ lи› kimbи› ko-o, и” tи›и›mi li bwiе‹ ya-a nи›и› si е‹kii le и” tи›и›mи”и” li fiana-a.
\v 3 Ntи›лқ ntuu е‹'woo bujи”е‹ е‹ge si bи›е‹waanи›е‹ bи›sи›е‹ bamu tи›лқ fи›si fи›ni be tee kii si и” lemи”и” li chи›и›е‹ li bи› sheлғе‹ ya chi. Fi se fiи›и› nи›и› chи›и›е‹ le и” bikи”и” chи›и›е‹.
\v 4 Fiee fimu nuuе‹ yи› lu fi nuuе‹ fi fи› nse ni е‹'wuki bujи”е‹ yи›ki le ni е‹'wuki le bи”и”е‹ bи› beе‹ biki baa chи›и›е‹ kи›.
\p 
\v 5 Sinи›е‹ wu sheлғе‹, nimи› chi и” nindi li bи›е‹waanи›е‹ bи›sи›е‹, teege li mfo-oе‹, baa и” ni и” nindi nи›и› tsaaе‹ lи›.
\v 6 Be tи›лқ tee li kintaashи› ki bи›niiе‹ bи› kimbeenchи›-и› ki lani kii kiе‹kи”е‹gisи› ko. ф† gwenini nи›и› и” fii bи›niiе‹ bи›lu lи› dze yi Nyи” wи›ki-i li dи›ndи› wu bee.
\v 7 ф† ni и” kii le be bo baa lи›kuuе‹ nuuе‹ kii bukooе‹ bu Krai, be bichi yи› le wi ni fii be wu nuuе‹ yи› bи› Nyи” kи›.
\v 8 Bи›dи›и›ni, tи› kи›mi le tи› ni tи› teendi bи›niiе‹ bи› beeyи›, ke se tи›и› be nuuе‹ bи›niiе‹ bи› nindi li fiee fimumkpa-aе‹ kii chи›и›е‹.
\s1 Kii Diotefи›s bи› Dи›mи›trus
\p 
\v 9 Ntи›лқ ntsи›и› fiee li kintaashи› ki bи›niiе‹ bи› kimbeenchи›-и› kinи›, fi se nuuе‹ le Diotefи›s wu kи”е‹gisi le ni tuuti mbaaе‹, tи›лқ mи›и›е‹ ki woo kи› li wi wu nuuе‹ mi-i kи›.
\v 10 Bи›dи›и›ni, е‹gii ke mi mbи›, nshiiki fiee fi feti fini fи›kwiiе‹. Si deе‹gi fiи›ti kimfiи›, tiiti jи›лғ yi bifi kii mi. Si feti lи›, mи›и›е‹и” nи›и› ki fukи› kи› bи› fi kи›. Fи›е‹gi mfiи› bи›е‹waanи›е‹ bи›sи›е‹, loosi tи› le kiiе‹ bи›niiе‹ bи› wи›ki le be ni be fii be, fi be kи›. Fи› be wи›ki le be ni be fii be, se tuu kuе‹gi be bu koе‹u lи› kintaashи› ki bи›niiе‹ bи› kimbeenchи›-и› lи›nti.
\p 
\v 11 Sinи›е‹ wu sheлғе‹, kiiе‹ и” ni и” biki fiee fi bifi kи›. ф† biki nuuе‹ fiee fi dzeeе‹. Wi wu feti fiee fi dzeeе‹ nuuе‹ wi wu Nyи”, wi wu feti fiee fi bifi nuuе‹ wi wu mи›и›е‹ ki kи›и› kи› Nyи” kи›.
\p 
\v 12 Dи›mи›trus wи› fiee wi wu bи›niiе‹ bи›chu tiiti biee bi dzeeе‹ kii wu, kiе‹ge kee ki dzeeе‹ se tiiti tи› kii wu. Tи› se tuu tи› tiiti tи› kii wu. ф† kii tи› le fiee fi tи› tiiti kii wu nuuе‹ chи›и›е‹.
\s1 N'yи›и›shи›
\p 
\v 13 Mи›и›е‹и” е‹kи›mi biee е‹ge le ntsи›и› li wи›-и›, se nuuе‹ le е‹kи”е‹gisi yи› le ntsи›и› tи› bи› fintiiе‹ fi kiе‹waati kи›.
\v 14 еҳiе‹gи”и” le shи›и” niiе‹ mbи› е‹и›е‹ wи›, tи› wи› se ni tи› yeti wi е‹iе‹gi wi li lii.
\p 
\v 15 Mbи›и›е‹gii ni nuuе‹ li wи›-и›. Nsaлғе‹ yi tи›и›wи› yи›и›shi yи›и› wи›. Yи›si mi li nsaлғе‹ yi tи›и›wи› chichi wi mumkpaе‹ mumkpaе‹.
